---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Our Approach - Proactive Accounting & Tax"
  description="Plan ahead, stay connected, and eliminate surprises. Our San Diego area CPA firm pairs proactive tax planning with integrated bookkeeping so you always know where things stand."
  path="/our-approach/"
  ogDescription="Plan ahead, stay connected, and eliminate surprises."
  ogImage="https://proactive-at.com/assets/img/IMG_Approach_Woman-working_1200x1800.webp"
>
  <!-- ======================= Page hero ======================= -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Our Approach</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= Intro ======================= -->
  <section class="split split--tight pattern-right">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split-col">
        <h2>Proactive + Connected for Real Business</h2>
        <div class="rich-text">
          <p>At Proactive Accounting &amp; Tax, our approach is simple:<br>plan ahead, stay connected, and eliminate surprises.</p>
          <p>Most accounting stress comes from reactivity &mdash; waiting until tax season to figure things out. We believe better outcomes come from thoughtful planning and clear communication throughout the year.</p>
          <p>Traditional tax work looks backward.<br>We focus forward.</p>
          <p>As a San Diego area CPA firm, we help clients make informed decisions before deadlines, filings, and problems arise. That&rsquo;s where clarity comes from &mdash; and where most tax savings actually happen.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="split-col split-media">
        <img src="/assets/img/IMG_Approach_Woman-working_1200x1800.webp" alt="Accountant working through a client's financials" width="600" height="900" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= One strategy ======================= -->
  <section class="center-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">One Strategy, Not Disconnected Advice</h2>
      <div class="rich-text">
        <p>Often business owners are forced to deal with fragmented support. They have a bookkeeper who doesn&rsquo;t interface with the CPA. A CPA who only shows up at tax time. And zero strategy when it comes to making real business decisions.</p>
        <p>Our approach centers on one coordinated strategy, led by your CPA, with an integrated financial team aligned around your goals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= Bookkeeping, integrated ======================= -->
  <section class="split split--inner linetop">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split-col">
        <p class="eyebrow">How bookkeeping is integrated</p>
        <h2 class="heading-sm">Bookkeeping That Supports Your Tax Strategy</h2>
        <div class="rich-text">
          <p>Ryan is a licensed bookkeeper as well as a CPA, and he personally handles bookkeeping for a select group of clients where it&rsquo;s the right fit.</p>
          <p>For most engagements, day-to-day bookkeeping is handled by trusted bookkeeping partners who meet our standards for accuracy, communication, and professionalism &mdash; with Ryan working closely with every bookkeeper on your account.</p>
          <p>Here&rsquo;s what matters:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your bookkeeper and CPA are aligned</li>
            <li>Your books support tax planning &mdash; not just reporting</li>
            <li>Issues are identified early, not at year-end</li>
            <li>You&rsquo;re not stuck coordinating between providers</li>
            <li>Ryan stays actively involved, reviewing the numbers, advising on strategy, and ensuring bookkeeping supports your tax goals.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You get the benefit of specialized bookkeeping and proactive tax oversight &mdash; without juggling relationships or repeating yourself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="split-col split-media">
        <img src="/assets/img/IMG_Approach_bookkeeping_1400.webp" alt="Bookkeeper organizing financial records" width="700" height="700" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= Proactive Tax Planning ======================= -->
  <section class="stacked linetop pattern-left">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stacked-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Clear Communication</p>
        <h2 class="heading-sm">Proactive Tax Planning</h2>
        <div class="rich-text">
          <p>A proactive approach only works with consistent communication.</p>
          <p>That means:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Clear explanations in plain English</li>
            <li>Guidance before decisions are made</li>
            <li>No disappearing act after tax season</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You&rsquo;ll always know where things stand and what to expect next.</p>
          <p>This approach is a strong fit if you:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Want a long-term CPA relationship</li>
            <li>Prefer planning ahead over reacting later</li>
            <li>Value clarity, coordination, and accountability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stacked-media">
        <img src="/assets/img/IMG_Approach_archetects_1000x812.webp" alt="Business partners planning together over documents" width="500" height="406" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
